items.title: Joe Satriani brings his G3 Tour to Mesa Arts Center
items.summary:
Danny Zelisko Presents G3 featuring Joe Satriani, Dream Theater’s John Petrucci and Def Leppard’s Phil Collen returns to the valley on January 18th at Mesa Arts Center at 7:30pm. Reserved seat tickets for the event go on sale Friday, October 6th at 10:00am at www.mesaartscenter.com. “G3 tours are always very exciting, challenging and a lot of fun for me,” says Satriani. “I love any chance I get to stand on stage and play for my!
